<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Your Donation</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #334155; line-height: 1.6;">
    <div style="max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <!-- Header -->
        <h1 style="color: #0f172a; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            Thank you, <%= name %>!
        </h1>

        <!-- Thank-you Message -->
        <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 16px;">
            We have successfully received your donation. Your support makes a big difference to our community!
        </p>

        <!-- Donation Details Card -->
        <div style="background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 28px 0;">
            <h2 style="color: #0f172a; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                Donation Details
            </h2>
            <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="font-size: 15px;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 8px;" width="130">Amount:</td>
                    <td style="color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; padding-bottom: 8px;"><%= amount %> EGP</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: #64748b;">Donation ID:</td>
                    <td style="color: #0f172a; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;"><%= donationId %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 16px;">
            Please keep the Donation ID above as a reference for your records. If you have any questions, feel free to reply directly to this email.
        </p>

        <!-- Footer / Sign-off -->
        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; padding-top: 24px; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 4px 0;">Best regards,</p>
            <strong style="color: #334155;">The Platform Team</strong>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
